461
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:11,060
If you say it's good, it's good, dude.

462
00:38:11,060 --> 00:38:13,820
Whenever I ask for something and can't get it, I'll have you ask instead.

463
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:17,720
