472
00:38:48,740 --> 00:38:50,780
Fine.

473
00:38:50,780 --> 00:38:52,480
Let's go inside.

474
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:54,340
Who's that, dude?

475
00:39:00,460 --> 00:39:02,220
Let's go inside.

476
00:39:04,300 --> 00:39:08,000
Ai'Tin, who's that?

477
00:39:20,560 --> 00:39:23,160
Isn't that your asshole brother?

478
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:28,520
Are you Tin's friend?

479
00:39:28,520 --> 00:39:31,540
My name is Tul. I'm Tin's older brother.

480
00:39:32,840 --> 00:39:34,840
Nice to meet you.

481
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:52,400
What's up?

482
00:39:52,940 --> 00:39:57,120
I'm glad to finally be able to meet my brother's important person.

483
00:39:59,740 --> 00:40:01,720
You're really such a...

484
00:40:01,720 --> 00:40:03,440
Tin!

485
00:40:08,640 --> 00:40:10,680
Don't mess with my guy.

486
00:40:15,040 --> 00:40:17,220
- Tin, I haven't even…
- Get in the house.

487
00:40:19,600 --> 00:40:22,820
- Tin.
- Get in the house.

488
00:40:22,820 --> 00:40:24,180
Please.

489
00:40:26,120 --> 00:40:28,260
Go. Wait for me inside.

490
00:40:30,700 --> 00:40:33,060
What a pretty naïve kid.

491
00:40:36,060 --> 00:40:37,800
Don't mess with him.

492
00:40:38,680 --> 00:40:40,740
Otherwise, don't say I didn't warn you.

493
00:41:04,330 --> 00:41:09,540
[Preview]

494
00:41:09,540 --> 00:41:10,660
Is Can home?

495
00:41:10,660 --> 00:41:13,880
